#: ../../S/speed-of-light.rst:5
msgid "speed of light"
msgstr "speed of light"

#: ../../S/speed-of-light.rst:7
msgid ""
"The absolutely fastest a particular algorithm or application could be "
"implemented, given a set of constraints that are assumed to be unchangeable."
" For example, \"This would take 60 microseconds without any processing "
"whatsoever, so that's the speed of light.\" However, as one brilliant hacker"
" once commented: \"Remember that the speed of light only is constant if you "
"can't redesign the universe.\""
msgstr ""
"変更不可能と仮定される一連の制約のもとで、特定のアルゴリズムやアプリケーションが実装されうる絶対的に最速のもの。たとえば「処理を一切しなくてもこれには60マイクロ秒かかるから、それが光速だ。」しかし、ある聡明なハッカーがかつて述べたように、「光速が一定なのは、宇宙を再設計できない場合に限ることを忘れるな。」"
